islike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"618c565fd22ac7ef5de250ec478c055857ec9fb6","tid":786292,"uid":184509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T05:43:38.000Z","msg":"50個既話要抽哂expect就係一樣<br />\n1/1+1/(49/50)+...+1/(1/50)<br />\n姐係1+1/((n-1)/n)...+1/(1/n)<br />\nExpect抽9成味加到45<br />\n1/1+...+1/(5/50)<br />\n姐係1+1/((n-1)/n)+...+1/(0.1n/n)<br />\n90%信心抽哂<br />\n要搵variance=(1-p)/p^2<br />\n姐係(1-1)/1^2+(1-49/50)/(49/50)^2+...+(1-1/50)/(1/50)^2<br />\n最後用expected次數+1.645xSD"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T05:49:10.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T05:56:08.000Z","msg":"Normal<br />\n<br />\nDiscrete照用normal,四捨五入啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T13:54:19.000Z","msg":"點解可以 assume 個 number of trials needed 大致上係 follow normal distribution？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2962000ddc0cb00b948dc5a26eb3520b2c53dbe4","tid":786292,"uid":184509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"86138feb207103eec366e3b453006e080ca6bbe0","tid":786292,"uid":72465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cce2c65a70a2538767ffd371788564b666b0f821","tid":786292,"uid":184509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"63922b3002e93219bb7576116d476bc0017302a6","tid":786292,"uid":199016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T05:49:10.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T05:56:08.000Z","msg":"Normal<br />\n<br />\nDiscrete照用normal,四捨五入啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T13:54:19.000Z","msg":"點解可以 assume 個 number of trials needed 大致上係 follow normal distribution？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T14:11:58.000Z","msg":"Law of large number嘛，而家抽既sample size夠大，所以會tend to normal，但都只不過係大致估算，學校應該都只會咁教<br />\n如果要計exact prob人手太複雜，例如要confirm exact第60果下先中第50款coupon既機率已經好麻煩，仲要加哂咁多個condition（50,51,52.....)先數到第幾下會累積到90% confidence...天光都未計完"},{"pid":"a7fc5882d4082048f606bbeae511b1a0e9c7d023","tid":786292,"uid":72465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T14:45:08.000Z","msg":"我想知原本個 distribution 係咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我原本係諗緊係每個 geometric variable 加埋晒一齊應該係 follow negative binomial distribution，即係 distribution of the number of Bernoulli trials needed for all 50 coupons；但係諗諗下唔係幾對路，因為每個 Bernoulli trial 個機率都唔一樣。<br />\n<br />\n但係如果直接講話係因為 law of large number 又好似太粗糙<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n始終唔係話隻隻 distribution 個 n 夠大就 approach normal distribution，要睇返個 distribution 本身係咩...學校學就係話 Binomial 啊 Poisson 啊 n夠大係嘅話用 normal distribution 去 estimate 係安全嘅，但係呢個 coupon collector's problem 又好似唔係呢兩個 distribution ~<br />\n<br />\n所以我諗緊有冇個嚴謹 D 嘅解釋？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申：只知皮毛<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57c804142564c7ca3fbb7c929a5954052584aad4","tid":786292,"uid":199016,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T14:50:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"15e2dd2ab30882208c1694b22718493358827c49","tid":786292,"uid":199016,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T14:55:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"61702fe869b53815fc140af18b150dc59493490b","tid":786292,"uid":199016,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T14:58:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"883